{"tid":1879071,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【慣性chur deadline】白宮聯署：阻止美國出售電槍，欠18,305，2月15日中午截止！","createTime":"2020-02-14T03:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T19:55:02.000Z","uid":90735,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d2dc161db8e509b244d5a8e553352f4cd7df70","tid":1879071,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人真係慣性deadline fighter<br />\n唔殺到埋身唔知死</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>請copy 呢段訊息去Whatsapp group廣傳</strong></span><br />\n休息夠未呀？快啲簽！<br />\n我哋嘅盟友美國人🇺🇸真係睇住白宮聯署嚟做嘢，✅通過人權法、🚫禁止武器出口等等<br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：阻止美國出售電槍<br />\n美國時間2月14日，<span style=\"color: red;\">即係香港時間 2月15日中午截止，欠18,305個簽名</span>，要簽爆10萬個！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=bd54d677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n唔好開分身簽名，否則check到可能被取消簽名</span></strong>[/quote]"},{"pid":"5a3ad4c8646730ef9f73a8603d61694a0bced19b","tid":1879071,"uid":119386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bd1e97377011927ee12fbdef86695e11c755596","tid":1879071,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets